data.description: Charming brick rancher in the heart of Colonial Heights!  This all brick home has fresh paint throughout, new counters in Kit, new flooring Kit, and much much more!  Upon entering the home you will notice the new roof, new soffit, and new gutters adding to the ease of maintenance that comes with living in an all brick home!  The foyer greets you with hardwood floors and takes you into the expansive Living/Dining combo.  A beautiful brick fireplace that is already plumbed for gas is a gorgeous focal point in this grand space.  Perfect for family gatherings.  The dining area connects to the charming kitchen space.  This space has TWO double closets that can be used as pantrys, newly painted cabinets, new laminate countertops, fresh paint on the walls, and brand new LVP. Cute! Just off the kitchen is a massive family gathering space for movie nights and Sunday games.  Right off the Family Room a well lit Sunroom is perfect for a home office space with access to the fenced in rear yard.  3 bedrooms, all with hardwood floors, are ample size and enhanced with double windows in all.  This home and it's convenient location will be a perfect gathering spot for all your family and friends!
